%3EThe%20findings%20offer%20encouraging%20evidence%20that%20people%20can%20safely%20exercise%20at%20a%20high%20intensity%20after%20a%20stroke.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20this%20study%20adds%20to%20a%20growing%20field%20of%20evidence%20that%20small-but-mighty%20workouts%20can%20pay%20big%20dividends%20for%20our%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22296f1a35-a15c-42ab-9fa0-a2dd06d96ae2%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20study%2C%20explained%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20McGill%20University%20and%20McMaster%20University%20in%20Canada%20studied%2082%20stroke%20survivors%2C%20between%2040%20and%2080%20years%20old%2C%20who%20underwent%20an%20exercise%20program.%20Both%20groups%20used%20a%20stepper%20exercise%20machine%2C%20and%20worked%20out%20three%20days%20a%20week%20for%2012%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20the%20participants%20were%20assigned%20a%2019-minute%2C%20high-intensity%20workout%20%E2%80%94%20fully%20exerting%20themselves%20for%20one%20minute%2C%20followed%20by%20one%20minute%20of%20gentle%20exercise%2C%20then%20repeating%20the%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20others%20did%20a%20moderate%20intensity%20workout%20%E2%80%94%2020-30%20minutes%20exercising%20at%2040-60%25%20heart%20rate%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20effort%20you%20might%20exert%20jogging.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20study%2C%20the%20high-intensity%20group%20saw%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20level%3C%2Fa%3E%20(measured%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvo2-max-explained-what-is-good-how-improve-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVO2%20max%3C%2Fa%3E)%20improve%20by%20twice%20as%20much%20as%20the%20moderate%20group.%20They%20also%20maintained%20the%20benefits%20at%20eight%20weeks%20of%20follow-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20right%20support%20and%20guidance%2C%20stroke%20survivors%20can%20safe