A%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20committed%20a%20costly%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20mistake%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20killing%20of%20Hamas%20political%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20in%20Tehran%20last%20week%2C%20Iran's%20acting%20foreign%20minister%20told%20AFP%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20act%20that%20the%20Zionists%20carried%20out%20in%20Tehran%20was%20a%20strategic%20mistake%20because%20it%20will%20cost%20them%20gravely%2C%26quot%3B%20Ali%20Bagheri%20said%20one%20day%20after%20attending%20an%20extraordinary%20session%20of%20the%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC)%20in%20the%20Saudi%20coastal%20city%20of%20Jeddah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Israel%20has%20not%20commented%20on%20Haniyeh's%20death%2C%20Iran%20has%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%2C%20setting%20the%20region%20on%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBagheri%20accused%20Israel%20of%20wanting%20%26quot%3Bto%20expand%20tension%2C%20war%20and%20conflict%20to%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20asserting%20it%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20fight%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Zionists%20are%20in%20no%20position%20to%20start%20a%20war%20against%20the%20Islamic%20Republic%20of%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20neither%20have%20the%20capacity%20nor%20the%20strength.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20on%20Wednesday%20of%20foreign%20ministers%20from%20the%2057-member%20OIC%20produced%20a%20declaration%20holding%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bfully%20responsible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bheinous%26quot%3B%20killing%20of%20Haniyeh%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Qatar%20and%20was%20a%20major%20player%20in%20talks%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20began%20with%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20southern%20Israel%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C198%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tall