nt%20to%20see%20what%20we%20can%20accomplish%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233a7c42b-0441-4a8a-9a64-70b45d8bf21b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20win%20and%20lose%20as%20a%20team%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20we%20fail%20%E2%80%94%20we%20fall%2C%20we%20drop%20the%20baton%2C%20and%20we%20get%20frustrated%20and%20discouraged.%20Instead%20of%20blaming%20each%20other%20or%20dwelling%20on%20our%20mistakes%2C%20we%20dust%20ourselves%20off%20and%20move%20on.%20Every%20day%20is%20another%20opportunity%20to%20%26quot%3Bshoot%20our%20shot.%26quot%3B%20Although%20we'll%20never%20earn%20a%20medal%20for%20our%20efforts%2C%20progressing%20toward%20our%20goal%20of%20a%20healthy%20relationship%20and%20family%20feels%20rewarding%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteammates-before-married-relationship-is-stronger-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723119543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b239ada5247369a3e9bed2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteammates-before-married-relationship-is-stronger-2024-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20met%20my%20husband%20while%20training%20around%20LSU's%20campus.%20Being%20teammates%20has%20helped%20our%20relationships%20in%20many%20ways.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Gumpert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteammates-before-married-relationship-is-stronger-2024-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Page%20Industries%20Q1%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%20to%20Rs%20165%20cr%20on%20strong%20demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723119509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F15%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400