0are%20in%20with%20authorities%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-updates-on-when-sheikh-hasina-will-leave-india-says-mea%2Farticleshow%2F112376244.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20updates'%20on%20when%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20will%20leave%20India%2C%20says%20MEA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723116498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112376272%2Cimgsize-855603.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fno-updates-on-when-sheikh-hasina-will-leave-india-says-mea%2Farticleshow%2F112376244.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fno-updates-on-when-sheikh-hasina-will-leave-india-says-mea%2Farticleshow%2F112376244.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BImagine%2C%20A%20Civic%20Body%20HQ%20Became%20Waqf%20Land%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%20Counters%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20handful%20of%20people%20captured%20Waqf%20boards%20in%20the%20country%20and%20ordinary%20Muslims%20did%20not%20get%20justice%2C%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20told%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20on%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Act%20that%20was%20introduced%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20said%20the%20provisions%20in%20the%20proposed%20law%20are%20based%20on%20multiple%20inquiry%20reports%20over%20the%20years%20and%20wide-ranging%20consultations%20with%20lakhs%20of%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bolster%20his%20arguments%2C%20he%20cited%20several%20instances%20of%20encroachment%20and%20illegality%20by%20Waqf%20bodies.%20%26quot%3BTiruchirapalli%20district%20is%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%201%2C500-year-old%20Sundareshwar%20temple%20is%20located%20there.%20There%2C%20a%20man%20went%20to%20sell%20his%20property%20and%20was%20told%20that%20his%20village%20is%20a%20Waqf%20property.%20Just%20imagine%2C%20the%20entire%20village%20has%20been%20declared%20Waqf%20property.%20Don't%20see%20religion%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20Surat%20Municipal%20Corporation.%20%26quot%3BSurat%20Municipal%20Corporation%20headquarters%20was%20declared%20Waqf%20property.%20Can%20you%20imagine%3F%20How%20can%20this%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20Buddhist%2C%20not%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim%2C%20but%20I%20respect%20all%20religions.%20Don't%20see%20this%20as%20a%20religious%20issue.%20Is%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20a%20private%20property%3F%20How%20can%20municipal%20property%20be%20declared%20Waqf%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20pointed%20to%20a%201976%20inquiry%20report%20that%20recommended%20steps%20to%20discipline%20Waqf%20boards.%20He%20referred%20to%20Sachar%20committee's%20recommendations%20for%20more%20representation%20in%20Waqf%20boards.%20%26quot%3BYou%20should%20be%20happy%2C%20you%20made%20this%20committee%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20Opposition%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20up%20the%20provision%20in%20the%20proposed%20law%20that%20provides%20for%20the%20representation%20of%20Shia%2C%20Sunni%2C%20Bohra%2C%20Agakhani%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%20among%20Muslims%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20community%20is%20crushing%20smaller%20communities%2C%20how%20can%20this%20Parliament%20allow%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20is%20rooting%20for%20a%20small%20section%20of%20people%20capturing%20power%20in%20these%20bodies%20and%20that%20there%20is%20widespread%20discontent%20within%20Muslims%20for%20Waqf%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20provisions%20in%20the%20Bill%20do%20not%20interfere%20with%20religious%20freedom%20or%20violate%20the%20Constitution%20in%20any%20way.%20The%20Centre%20has%20agreed%20to%20send%20the%20legislation%20to%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee%20for%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20claimed%20that%20many%20leaders%20in%20the%20Opposition%20had%20privately%20told%20him%20that%20state%20Waqf%20boards%20had%20turned%20into%20mafia.%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20take%20their%20names%20and%20destroy%20their%20political%20careers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Opposition%20targeted%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20proposed%20changes%20over%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill.%20Congress's%20KC%20Venugopal%20termed%20the%20proposed%20law%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20federal%20system.%20He%20also%20opposed%20the%20provision%20of%20appointing%20non-Muslim%20members%20to%20Waqf%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20second-largest%20Opposition%20force%2C%20also%20opposed%20the%20Bill.%20%26quot%3BNo%20person%20from%20outside%20the%20community%20is%20part%20of%20other%20religious%20bodies.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20including%20non-Muslims%20in%20Waqf%20bodies%3F%26quot%3B%20party%20chief%20and%20MP%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20the%20legislation%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20BJP%20ally%20JDU%2C%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20said%20the%20Bill%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20make%20the%20functioning%20of%20Waqf%20boards%20transparent.%20Countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Bill%20is%20against%20minorities%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%201984%20anti-Sik%20riots%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20assassination%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BWho%20killed%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723116360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fei917lcg_kiren-rijiju-_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkiren-rijiju-waqf-amendment-bill-imagine-a-civic-body-hq-became-waqf-land-minister-counters-opposition-6292478%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20handful%20of%20people%20captured%20Waqf%20boards%20in%20the%20country%20and%20ordinary%20Muslims%20did%20not%20get%20justice%2C%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20told%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20on%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Act%20that%20was%20introduced%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkiren-rijiju-waqf-amendment-bill-imagine-a-civic-body-hq-became-waqf-land-minister-counters-opposition-6292478%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Interference%20In%20Any%20Religious%20Body%26quot%3B%3A%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20Defends%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20joined%20ranks%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20The%20legislation%20aims%20to%20address%20issues%20related%20to%20powers%20of%20State%20Waqf%20Boards%2C%20registration%20and%20survey%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20and%20removal%20of%20encroachment.%C2%A0Union%20Minority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20later%20proposed%20sending%20the%20Bill%20to%20a%20joint%20parliamentary%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20proposes%20to%20amend%2044%20sections%20of%20the%201995%20Waqf%20Act.%20The%20Bill%20proposes%20that%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20and%20state%20Waqf%20Boards%20must%20have%20two%20women.%20It%20also%20lays%20down%20that%20money%20received%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20must%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20widows%2C%20divorcees%2C%20and%20orphans%20in%20the%20manner%20suggested%20by%20the%20government.%20Another%20key%20proposal%20is%20that%20women's%20inheritances%20must%20be%20protected.%20The%20provision%20for%20including%20non-Muslim%20members%20of%20Waqf%20bodies%20is%20another%20contentious%20point%20in%20the%20proposed%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20of%20the%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Congress's%20KC%20Venugopal%20termed%20the%20proposed%20law%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20is%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20federal%20system.%20He%20also%20opposed%20the%20provision%20of%20appointing%20non-Muslim%20members%20to%20Waqf%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20second-largest%20Opposition%20force%2C%20has%20also%20opposed%20the%20Bill.%20%26quot%3BThis%20Bill%20has%20been%20introduced%20as%20part%20of%20well-thought-out%20politics.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20democratic%20process%20for%20election%2C%20why%20nominate%20people.%20No%20person%20from%20outside%20the%20community%20is%20part%20of%20other%20religious%20bodies.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20including%20non-Muslims%20in%20Waqf%20bodies%3F%26quot%3B%20party%20chief%20and%20MP%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnother%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Mohibbullah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20injustice%20to%20Muslims.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20going%20to%20commit%20a%20huge%20mistake%2C%20we%20will%20suffer%20because%20of%20this%20Bill%20for%20centuries.%20This%20is%20interference%20with%20religion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20sell%20of%20lands%20belonging%20to%20Waqf%20boards%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20amendments.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20amendments%20of%20the%20'Waqf%20Board'%20are%20just%20an%20excuse%3B%20Selling%20lands%20like%20defence%2C%20railway%20and%20Nazul%20land%20is%20the%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20While%20Trinamool's%20Sudip%20Bandhyopadhyay%20said%20the%20legislation%20is%20against%20federalism%2C%20DMK's%20K%20Kanimozhi%20said%20it%20is%20against%20the%20minority%20community.%20%26quot%3BWill%20it%20be%20possible%20for%20Christian%20and%20Muslim%20to%20handle%20Hindu%20temples%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20the%20legislation%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20leader%20of%20BJP%20ally%20JDU%2C%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20Singh%2C%20said%20the%20Bill%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20make%20the%20functioning%20of%20Waqf%20boards%20transparent.%20Countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20Bill%20is%20against%20minorities%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%201984%20anti-Sik%20riots%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20assassination%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BWho%20killed%20thousands%20of%20Sikhs%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupriya%20Sule%20of%20NCP's%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20said%20the%20government%20did%20not%20carry%20out%20detailed%20consultation%20before%20bringing%20the%20Bill%20to%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20send%20this%20to%20the%20standing%20committee%20for%20better%20consultation.%20The%20timing%20is%20of%20concern.%20What%20happened%20suddenly%20in%20Waqf%20board%20that%20you%20have%20to%20bring%20the%20Bill%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EET%20Mohammed%20Basheer%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union%20Muslim%20League%20and%20K%20Radhakrishan%20of%20the%20CPM%20opposed%20the%20Bill%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20opposed%20the%20legislation%2C%20calling%20it%20discriminatory%20and%20a%20grave%20attack%20on%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20as%20it%20violates%20judicial%20independence.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Government%20has%20sought%20to%20severely%20restrict%20how%20Muslims%20can%20manage%20their%20Waqf%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinority%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%20said%20the%20government%20had%20to%20bring%20amendments%20because%20previous%20Congress%20governments%20could%20not%20address%20issues%20in%20the%20law.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20you%20couldn't%20do%2C%20we%20had%20to%20bring%20these%20amendments.%20We%20are%20elected%20representatives%2C%20support%20this%20bill%20and%20you%20will%20get%20blessings%20of%20crores%20of%20people.%20Some%20people%20have%20captured%20Waqf%20boards%20and%20this%20Bill%20has%20been%20brought%20to%20give%20justice%20to%20ordinary%20Muslims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20claimed%20that%20many%20leaders%20in%20the%20Opposition%20had%20privately%20told%20him%20that%20state%20waqf%20boards%20had%20turned%20into%20mafia.%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20take%20their%20names%20and%20destroy%20their%20political%20careers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723115820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fr3rrpv4_kiren-rijiju-venugopal-split_625x300_08_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-protests-waqf-bill-which-proposes-women-non-muslims-on-board-6290710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20parties%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20joined%20ranks%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fopposition-protests-waqf-bill-which-proposes-women-non-muslims-on-board-6290710%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BViolation%20Of%20Freedom%20Of%20Religion%26quot%3B%3A%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20Shreds%20Waqf%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAsaduddin%20Owaisi%20of%20AIMIM%20(All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen)%20ripped%20into%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20bill%20presented%20in%20parliament%20today%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Barbitrary%26quot%3B.%20The%20bill%2C%20he%20said%2C%20interferes%20with%20the%20fundamental%20Right%20to%20Freedom%20of%20Religion%20enshrined%20in%20the%20constitution%2C%20and%20would%20help%20the%20government%20take%20over%20not%20only%20Waqf%20properties%20but%20also%20those%20belonging%20to%20dargahs%20and%20mosques.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20law%2C%20which%20envisages%20changes%20to%20the%20existing%20version%20on%2044%20points%2C%20has%20already%20been%20criticised%20as%20%26quot%3Bdraconian%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20law%20limits%20the%20right%20of%20a%20person%20to%20will%20their%20property%20or%20dispose%20it.%20But%20look%20at%20what%20you%20are%20doing%20-%20Hindus%20can%20give%20complete%20property%20to%20daughter%20or%20son.%20I%20as%20a%20Muslim%20can%20only%20give%20one-third.%20I%20can%20gift%20but%20cannot%20give%20it%20to%20Allah.%20You%20are%20stopping%20me%20from%20praying.%20You%20are%20restraining%20work%20for%20Allah%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%20he%20took%20on%20a%20provision%20that%20bars%20converts%20for%20less%20than%20five%20years%20from%20donating%20to%20Waqf.%20%26quot%3BTo%20insist%20that%20a%20person%20has%20been%20practicing%20for%20five%20years%20--%20how%20can%20this%20be%20verified%3F%20Who%20will%20decide%3F%20Does%20a%20new%20convert%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20five%20years%20to%20donate%3F%20Isn't%20that%20a%20violation%20of%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Owaisi%20said%20in%20a%20sharp%20takedown%20of%20the%20proposed%20amendments.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20rule%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%20or%20people%20belonging%20to%20any%20other%20religions.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723115460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F8nhhfmro_asaduddin-owaisi_625x300_08_Augu