d%20Georgia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20race%20has%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20Corey%20Lewandowski%2C%20a%20longtime%20adviser%20to%20the%20former%20president%2C%20told%20Reuters%2C%20though%20he%20said%20the%20race%20still%20favors%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20that%20wanted%20to%20very%20actively%20run%20against%20Joe%20Biden.%20We%20felt%20very%20good%20about%20our%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublicly%2C%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20have%20tried%20vigorously%20to%20cast%20Harris%2C%20a%20Californian%2C%20as%20an%20out-of-touch%20liberal%20and%20link%20her%20to%20unpopular%20Biden%20policies%20on%20immigration%20and%20inflation.%20They%20say%20it%20matters%20little%20whether%20they%20are%20facing%20Biden%20or%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20nine%20sources%20told%20Reuters%20they%20see%20Harris%20as%20a%20far%20tougher%20opponent%20than%20Biden%2C%20who%20had%20been%20struggling%20for%20months%20in%20the%20face%20of%20doubts%20about%20his%20mental%20acuity%20and%20weakening%20poll%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20change%20the%20map%20as%20much%20as%20shrink%20it.%20Now%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20talk%20about%20places%20like%20New%20Jersey%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Trump%20campaign%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20internal%20campaign%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuters%20interviewed%2012%20campaign%20staff%2C%20advisers%20and%20donors%20who%20described%20a%20campaign%20that%20is%20grasping%20for%20a%20fresh%20strategy%20as%20it%20confronts%20a%20younger%2C%20more%20dynamic%20Democratic%20candidate%20who%20has%20energized%20the%20Democratic%20base%20and%20raised%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clear%20to%20everyone%20she%20could%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20senior%20Trump%20adviser%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20more%20freely%20discuss%20internal%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20shrinking%20battleground%20map%2C%20the%20Trump%20team%20said%20its%20strategy%20hadn't%20changed%20since%20Harris%20became%20the%20Democratic%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTeam%20Trump%20has%20ads%20in%20every%20battleground%20state%2C%20we%20have%20expanded%20the%20political%20map%20to%20include%20traditional%20'blue%20states'%20like%20Minnesota%20and%20Virginia%20with%20staff%20on%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20Republican%20Party%20spokesperson%20Anna%20Kelly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmmar%20Moussa%2C%20a%20Harris%20campaign%20spokesman%2C%20said%20Trump%20and%20Vance%20were%20taking%20the%20country%20backwards%2C%20while%20Harris%20was%20taking%20the%20country%20forwards.%20He%20did%20not%20address%20the%20electoral%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20sources%20Reuters%20spoke%20to%20pointed%20to%20three%20issues%3A%20delays%20in%20rolling%20out%20attack%20ads%20against%20Harris%2C%20which%20are%20seen%20as%20key%20for%20pointing%20out%20an%20opponent's%20perceived%20weaknesses%3B%20doubts%20among%20some%20Republican%20leaders%20and%20donors%20over%20the%20selection%20of%20Senator%20JD%20Vance%20as%20running%20mate%3B%20and%20concerns%20over%20Trump%20himself%20as%20he%20tramples%20over%20his%20advisers'%20efforts%20to%20define%20Harris%20based%20on%20her%20policy%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20source%20said%20the%20anti-Harris%20ads%20had%20been%20slow%20to%20air%20in%20part%20because%20the%20material%20had%20to%20be%20run%20by%20focus%20groups%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20also%20wanted%20to%20see%20who%20Harris%20would%20pick%20as%20her%20running%20mate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20source%20briefed%20on%20the%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20this%20week%20announced%20Minnesota%20Governor%20Tim%20Walz%2C%20a%20plain-speaking%20midwesterner%2C%20as%20her%20vice%20presidential%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMAY%20MEMO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20May%2C%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20had%20started%20gaming%20out%20the%20possibility%20that%20Harris%20or%20another%20Democrat%20could%20replace%20Biden%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ticket%2C%20according%20to%20an%20internal%20memo%20from%20campaign%20staffer%20Austin%20McCubbin%20shared%20with%20senior%20advisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2012-page%20memo%2C%20which%20was%20reviewed%20by%20Reuters%2C%20outlined%20the%20Democratic%20Party's%20rules%20for%20replacing%20a%20presidential%20candidate%20and%20possible%20scenarios%2C%20including%20Biden%20stepping%20down%20voluntarily%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Binsider%20rebellion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20did%20not%20detail%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20a%20Harris%20candidacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETony%20Fabrizio%2C%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20pollster%2C%20predicted%20in%20a%20memo%20released%20to%20the%20press%20last%20month%20that%20Harris%20would%20enjoy%20a%20short-term%20polling%20boost%2C%20but%20that%20the%20race%20would%20then%20settle%20down.%20%26quot%3BHarris'%20'honeymoon'%20will%20end%20and%20voters%20will%20refocus%20on%20her%20role%20as%20Biden's%20partner%20and%20co-pilot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lead-up%20to%20Biden's%20exit%2C%20the%20Trump-aligned%20MAGA%20Inc%20super%20PAC%20readied%20a%20TV%20ad%20accusing%20Harris%20of%20covering%20up%20Biden's%20infirmity.%20It%20began%20airing%20in%20four%20swing%20states%20on%20July%2021%2C%20the%20day%20Biden%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20ending%20his%20reelection%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20campaign%20found%20itself%20on%20the%20defensive%20over%20Trump's%20selection%20of%20Vance%20as%20his%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%20has%20faced%20a%20wave%20of%20negative%20press%20over%20past%20comments%20referring%20to%20some%20Democrats%2C%20including%20Harris%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20childless%20cat%20ladies%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20insult%20seen%20as%20misogynistic%20and%20dismissive%20of%20people%20without%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20National%20Committee%20and%20the%20campaign%20have%20been%20fielding%20calls%20from%20some%20donors%20who%20fear%20Vance%20has%20become%20a%20distraction%20and%20is%20dragging%20the%20ticket%20down%2C%20according%20to%20two%20sources%20aware%20of%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20campaign%20focuses%20on%20a%20smaller%20map%2C%20Vance%20is%20expected%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20relatively%20conservative%20and%20rural%20places%2C%20particularly%20in%20Rust%20Belt%20states%2C%20like%20Michigan%20and%20Pennsylvania%2C%20where%20his%20rural%20roots%20and%20concerns%20about%20industrial%20decay%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20resonate%20with%20voters%2C%20according%20to%20four%20sources%20close%20to%20the%20campaign%20or%20vice%20presidential%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Vance%20has%20held%20press%20conferences%20near%20Harris-Walz%20campaign%20events%20in%20Wisconsin%20and%20Michigan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETRUMP%20ATTACKS%20HARRIS%20-%20AND%20HIS%20ALLIES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20Trump's%20resort%20to%20name-calling%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20Harris'%20policy%20positions.%20Trump%20has%20cycled%20furiously%20through%20a%20series%20of%20personal%20insults%20against%20Harris.%20Those%20efforts%20have%20generated%20negative%20headlines%20-%20about%20Trump%2C%20rather%20than%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20an%20event%20for%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Black%20Journalists%20last%20week%2C%20Trump%20questioned%20whether%20Harris%20-%20whose%20mother%20was%20born%20in%20India%20and%20whose%20father%20was%20born%20in%20Jamaica%20-%20was%20actually%20Black.%20That%20left%20donors%20and%20aides%20baffled%20and%20alarmed%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Republican%20donor%2C%20an%20operative%20at%20a%20pro-Trump%20super%20PAC%20spending%20group%2C%20and%20a%20Trump-supporting%20union%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20Trump%20attacked%20Georgia's%20Republican%20governor%2C%20Brian%20Kemp%2C%20at%20a%20rally%2C%20possibly%20alienating%20a%20popular%20figure%20in%20a%20battleground%20state%20where%20Trump%20could%20need%20help%20mobilizing%20voters%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20been%20firing%20off%20multiple%2C%20convoluted%20missives%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20app%2C%20including%20one%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20which%20he%20mused%20about%20Biden%20returning%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20spring%20and%20earlier%20this%20summer%2C%20as%20public%20opinion%20polls%20showed%20Trump%20expanding%20his%20lead%20over%20Biden%20in%20battleground%20states%2C%20the%20former%20president%20did%20events%20in%20what%20had%20been%20considered%20safe%20Democratic%20areas%20-%20Minnesota%2C%20Virginia%2C%20even%20New%20York%20City%20-%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20expand%20the%20electoral%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20last%20Saturday%2C%20Trump%20was%20back%20to%20basics%3A%20campaigning%20in%20Georgia%2C%20where%20polls%20showed%20the%20race%20had%20tightened%20after%20Harris'%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20is%20going%20to%20be%20fiercely%20competitive%2C%20with%20Trump%20clinging%20to%20a%20slight%20edge%20thanks%20to%20support%20from%20some%20Black%20voters%2C%20said%20Mark%20Rountree%2C%20a%20Georgia%20pollster%20who%20is%20not%20affiliated%20with%20either%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Trump%20is%20getting%20outspent%20on%20campaign%20ads%20in%20battleground%20states%2C%20according%20to%20AdImpact%2C%20a%20firm%20that%20tracks%20campaign%20ad%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20and%20affiliated%20committees%20have%20outspent%20Trump%20and%20his%20allies%20%24112%20million%20to%20%2470.1%20million%20on%20ads%20since%20July%2022%2C%20according%20to%20AdImpact%20data%2C%20although%20Trump%20has%20matched%20Harris'%20outlays%20in%20Pennsylvania%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20crucial%20state%20for%20each%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20future%20reservations%20of%20TV%20air%20time%2C%20Harris%20and%20her%20allies%20are%20swamping%20Trump%20%24172.4%20million%20to%20%2471.8%20million%20as%20of%20this%20week%2C%20the%20firm%20said%2C%20although%20those%20figures%20are%20likely%20to%20change%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20most%20telling%20was%20the%20Trump%20campaign's%20significant%20new%20ad%20buy%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20which%20had%20looked%20likely%20to%20remain%20Republican%20until%20Harris'%20ascension%20energized%20Black%20and%20young%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20putting%20money%20in%20there%20now%20in%20the%20hope%20she%20decides%20to%20leave%20it%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justin%20Sayfie%2C%20a%20Republican%20lobbyist%20and%20Trump%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20is%20already%20up%20on%20the%20air%20in%20the%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723113840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F06lu95io_kamala-harris-donald-trump-afp_625x300_03_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-the-kamala-harris-surge-has-scrambled-trumps-battle-plan-6292141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20little%20over%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidential%20campaign%20had%20visions%20of%20an%20expansive%20national%20strategy%20that%20would%20result%20in%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-the-kamala-harris-surge-has-scrambled-trump