0been%20living%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20wanted%20to%20take%20me%20there.%20I%20had%20taken%20permission%20from%20my%20coaches%20to%20go%20with%20her%2C%20as%20I%20wasn't%20feeling%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20me%20permission%20and%20I%20came%20to%20the%20hotel.%20When%20I%20came%20here%2C%20I%20needed%20some%20of%20my%20stuff%20which%20was%20still%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Village.%20As%20I%20was%20unwell%2C%20I%20slept.%20My%20sister%20took%20my%20accreditation%20card%20and%20went%20to%20the%20village.%20She%20asked%20the%20authorities%20there%20if%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20get%20my%20stuff%20from%20the%20village.%20The%20authorities%20took%20away%20the%20accreditation%20card%20from%20her%20and%20took%20her%20to%20the%20police%20station%20for%20verification.%20This%20was%20the%20only%20reason%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20I%20wasn't%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntim%20also%20revealed%20that%20her%20sister%20was%20released%20by%20the%20police%20soon%20after%20the%20verification%20was%20completed%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20verification%20was%20done%2C%20my%20sister%20was%20sent%20back%20with%20the%20accreditation%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rumour%20about%20Antim's%20coaches%20getting%20into%20a%20fight%20with%20a%20cab%20driver%20also%20surfaced.%20She%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20incident%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20said%20that%20my%20coach%20fought%20with%20a%20driver%20but%20that%20isn't%20true%20either.%20My%20coaches%20were%20just%20upset%20with%20my%20loss.%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20booked%20their%20cab.%20They%20came%20to%20the%20hotel%20but%20got%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20trouble%20because%20of%20a%20language%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wanted%20to%20come%20to%20the%20hotel%20to%20collect%20money%20(Euros)%20but%20some%20miscommunication%20happened%20with%20the%20cab%20driver.%