e%20women%20seeking%20justice.%20His%20team%20followed%20up%20with%20us%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20every%20step.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20Batman%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20it%20for%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work%20but%20never%20to%20its%20fruits.%20Let%20not%20the%20fruits%20of%20action%20be%20your%20motive%2C%20nor%20let%20your%20attachment%20be%20to%20inaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20his%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20candidly%20accepts%20that%20while%20saying%20it%20is%20easy%2C%20there%20are%20difficult%20days.%20But%20knowing%20that%20this%20is%20the%20right%20path%20helps%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSocial%20workers%20should%20forgo%20the%20thought%20of%20any%20personal%20gain%20from%20their%20work.%20This%20work%20is%20strictly%20for%20society%2C%20and%20any%20kind%20of%20expectations%20will%20only%20serve%20to%20bring%20it%20down.%20The%20moment%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20anything%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20free%20yourself%20up%20to%20truly%20do%20everything.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%20go%20by%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20devastation%20at%20Abraham%E2%80%99s%20death%20made%20it%20very%20important%20for%20him%20to%20help%20anyone%20he%20could.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20doing.%20While%20Bengaluru%20is%20swarming%20with%20tech%20bros%2C%20we%20need%20more%20Brosephs%20across%20the%20country.%20Perhaps%20we%20should%20consider%20emulating%20his%20selfless%20actions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20help%20him%2C%20you%20could%20donate%20to%20broseph%40upi.%20You%20can%20also%20join%20his%20army%20by%20visiting%20the%20website%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flinktr.ee%2FSt_Broseph%5C%22%3Ebroseph.in.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Dushyant