20of%20explaining%20that%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20few%20months%20were%20difficult%20as%20he%20remembers%20%E2%80%9Clooking%20at%20the%20fan%E2%80%9D%20and%20surviving%20on%20the%20savings%20he%20had!%20Chandrashekhar%20then%20started%20looking%20for%20government%20schemes%20and%20loans%20that%20he%20could%20apply%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20registering%20%E2%80%98Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20Private%20Limited%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20found%20his%20first%20investor%20in%20an%20incubator%20in%20Pune.%20The%20startup%20received%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20August%202021%2C%20kicking%20off%20a%20series%20of%20grants%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20the%20website%20and%20application%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20technical%20aspects%2C%20the%20founder%20had%20a%20big%20task%20in%20hand%3A%20getting%20customers%20and%20workers%20to%20sign%20up.%20After%20hiring%20seven%20members%20for%20his%20team%2C%20the%20next%20challenge%20was%20wooing%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20for%20blue-collar%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20labour%20%3Cem%3Echowks%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20a%20mobile%20shop%20or%20small%20grocery%20store%20nearby%2C%20Digital%20Labour%20Chowk%20signed%20up%20these%20shop%20owners%20as%20business%20associates.%20They%20would%20help%20workers%20register%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9EWHhrCBDV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E